16:42.282 --> 16:44.241
You throw quite a party.

16:44.266 --> 16:46.033
[Chuckles] Thanks, Felicia.

16:46.058 --> 16:48.020
Unfortunately, we need to get going.

16:48.588 --> 16:50.903
But it certainly has been exciting.

16:50.928 --> 16:52.030
Oh.

16:53.462 --> 16:54.876
Jerry, now.

17:01.384 --> 17:02.668
Do you know why they're leaving?

17:02.702 --> 17:03.912
Well, it's not to have sex.

17:03.937 --> 17:05.702
That guy wouldn't stop
staring at the waiters.

17:05.727 --> 17:06.913
[Both chuckle]

17:06.938 --> 17:09.319
They're leaving because naked
men are serving Tequila shots

17:09.345 --> 17:11.731
in a home decorating store at 6:30.

17:11.756 --> 17:13.556
Or as I call it, Monday.

17:13.878 --> 17:16.201
Speaking of which, I
could use a shot right now.

17:17.147 --> 17:18.648
[Groans]

17:21.686 --> 17:23.153
- Ooh!
- Ohh!

17:23.188 --> 17:24.717
- I'm so sorry.
- No, my fault.

17:24.742 --> 17:25.747
[Chuckles]

17:25.771 --> 17:28.892
Um... You're, uh, April, right?

17:28.961 --> 17:31.044
- This is your party.
- Guilty as charged.

17:31.069 --> 17:32.947
Oh, no. What? Are you
kidding me? This is great.

17:32.972 --> 17:35.506
Someone was saying that
you, uh, own this store.

17:35.564 --> 17:36.574
I do.

17:36.643 --> 17:39.412
Though this is not what
it normally looks like.

17:39.837 --> 17:41.238
Well, I'd love to see it someday

17:41.272 --> 17:43.073
when it's not so...

17:43.108 --> 17:44.778
Both: "Eyes wide shut."

17:45.106 --> 17:47.074
[Both chuckle]

17:48.246 --> 17:50.530
Can I get you, uh, a free drink?

17:50.948 --> 17:52.882
- Yes.
- Look at this.

17:55.285 --> 17:56.798
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

18:01.625 --> 18:04.093
